<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Νεμεσιανὸς Κολλούθω τῷ φιλτάτῳ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>ὁ Σύρος πρὸ πολλοῦ τὸ τάλαντον εἴληφε καὶ Νεῖλος ἔτι πάλαι 

    <lb n="3"/><expan><ex cert="high">τάλαντον</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="700">ψ</num>, καὶ τὰς λοιπὰς δὲ αὐτῷ μετεβαλόμεθα· μὴ οὖν ταρασσέτω 

    <lb n="4"/>πρὸς ἡμᾶς τοσούτῳ χρόνῳ ἀμέ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μπτ</unclear>ως ἡμῖν κοινων<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ῦντα· 

    <lb n="5"/>τὴν δὲ λοιπάδα οὐκ ἐν πολλῷ οὖσαν τοῖς λινο<hi rend="diaeresis">ύ</hi>φοις τήρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">η</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σο</supplied>ν 

    <lb n="6"/>μηδὲν βλαπτόμενος· ἐν γὰρ τούτοις αἱ σπουδαὶ τῶν 

    <lb n="7"/>φίλων φαίνονται. <note lang="en" anchored="yes" place="not specified">m2 ?</note> ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι. </ab></div><div n="meta.30344" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30344" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="201" notAfter="400">III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.30344" type="commentary" subtype="mentionedDates" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head></div><div n="meta.30344" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">42</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3086</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">30344</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">42</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3086</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;42;3086" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30344" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.30344" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName type="ancientFindspot" cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.30344" type="figure" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASHdcda76683cedda61cfe721"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></t